<lb ed="D" n="0009a07"/><p xml:id="pD10p0009a0701" cb:type="dharani">那慕<g ref="#CB16765"/>婆怛他揭多<note place="inline">去</note>喃<note place="inline">去</note><note place="inline">一</note>　唵<note place="inline">二</note>　肥布
<lb ed="D" n="0009a08"/>羅孽<g ref="#CB22016"/><note place="inline">三</note>　摩尼<note place="inline">去</note>鉢臘<note place="inline">二合</note><g ref="#CB22016"/><note place="inline">四</note>　怛他多
<lb ed="D" n="0009a09"/><note place="inline">去</note>那捺<g ref="#CB08859"/>舎泥<note place="inline">五</note>　摩尼摩尼<note place="inline">六</note>　蘇鉢臘
<lb ed="D" n="0009a10"/><g ref="#CB22016"/><note place="inline">七</note>　肥摩麗<note place="inline">八</note>　娑孽囉鉗鼻曬<note place="inline">九</note>　吽吽
<lb ed="D" n="0009a11"/><note place="inline">十</note>　什皤羅什皤羅<note place="inline">十一</note>　㪍陀嚩𡀔枳羝<note place="inline">十二</note>
<lb ed="D" n="0009a12"/>　麌<note place="inline">遇羽切</note>醯夜<note place="inline">二合</note>地瑟恥<note place="inline">二合</note>多孽<g ref="#CB22016"/><note place="inline">十三</note>　莎
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0010a" n="0010a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0010a01"/>訶<note place="inline">十四</note></p>
<lb ed="D" n="0010a02"/><p xml:id="pD10p0010a0201">念此陀羅尼者則為以諸微妙香華塗
<lb ed="D" n="0010a03"/>香末香供養十方一切諸佛若能讀誦
<lb ed="D" n="0010a04"/>即得不退轉無上正覺百千萬劫一切
<lb ed="D" n="0010a05"/>如來讚不能盡一切魔王<g ref="#CB29806"/>神等不能
<lb ed="D" n="0010a06"/>為害增長無量福德。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0010a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">心呪</cb:mulu><head>心呪</head><p xml:id="pD10p0010a0703" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">唵　摩<g ref="#CB08859"/>跋杜黎吽</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0010a08"/><p xml:id="pD10p0010a0801">若誦一十萬徧得見一切如來誦二十
<lb ed="D" n="0010a09"/>萬徧見一切佛土乃至誦一百萬徧得
<lb ed="D" n="0010a10"/>一切佛灌頂佛地與一切佛同會如是
<lb ed="D" n="0010a11"/>陪勝若造五逆謗法等罪誦呪千徧皆
<lb ed="D" n="0010a12"/>得消滅得不退位增無量功德。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0011a" n="0011a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">隨心呪</cb:mulu><head>隨心呪</head><p xml:id="pD10p0011a0104" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">唵　摩尼達哩吽泮吒</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a02"/><p xml:id="pD10p0011a0201">若誦一萬徧所有為障閡<g ref="#CB29806"/>神皆來敬
<lb ed="D" n="0011a03"/>禮為使乃至誦十萬徧得盡見過去諸
<lb ed="D" n="0011a04"/>佛所求無閡。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">七俱胝佛母準泥大明陀羅尼</cb:mulu><head>七俱胝佛母準泥大明陀羅尼<note place="inline">知字函</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a06"/><p xml:id="pD10p0011a0601" cb:type="dharani">那麼䬃哆喃<note place="inline">一</note><note place="inline">去</note>　三<note place="inline">去</note>藐三沒陀俱胝南
<lb ed="D" n="0011a07"/><note place="inline">二</note>　怛姪<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB08859"/>也</note>他<note place="inline">三</note>　唵<note place="inline">四</note>　左<g ref="#CB27601"/><note place="inline">五</note>　祖<g ref="#CB27601"/><note place="inline">六</note>　準
<lb ed="D" n="0011a08"/>泥<note place="inline">七</note>　莎嚩訶<note place="inline">八</note></p>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a09"/><p xml:id="pD10p0011a0901">若有四眾受持讀誦此陀羅尼滿九十
<lb ed="D" n="0011a10"/>萬徧無量劫來五無閒等一切諸罪悉
<lb ed="D" n="0011a11"/>滅無餘所在生處皆得值遇諸佛菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0011a12"/>所有資具隨意充足無量百生常得出
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0012a" n="0012a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a01"/>家若是在家菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>修持戒行堅固不退
<lb ed="D" n="0012a02"/>速得成就無上菩提恒生天上常為諸
<lb ed="D" n="0012a03"/>天之所愛敬。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">禮拜滅罪呪</cb:mulu><head>禮拜滅罪呪<note place="inline">過字函</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a05"/><p xml:id="pD10p0012a0501" cb:type="dharani">那<note place="inline">上</note>謨菩<note place="inline">上</note>陀夜烏牟戶嚕戶嚕徙<note place="inline">穌孔
<lb ed="D" n="0012a06"/>切</note>䭾盧者<g ref="#CB08859"/>娑<note place="inline">上</note>囉皤囉他<note place="inline">上</note>娑䭾<g ref="#CB08859"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a07"/>娑<note place="inline">上</note>嚩訶</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a08"/><p xml:id="pD10p0012a0801">誦呪一徧禮佛一拜勝禮千億拜<unclear/><unclear/>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a09"/>德又云命終諸佛來迎呪<note place="inline">婆羅門僧多誦</note>。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a10"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">金剛壽命陀羅尼</cb:mulu><head>金剛壽命陀羅尼<note place="inline">書字函</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a11"/><p xml:id="pD10p0012a1101" cb:type="dharani">唵　嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>俞曬　娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0012a12"/><p xml:id="pD10p0012a1201">若有受持此呪日各三時時別千徧過
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0013a" n="0013a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a01"/>去所有惡業因緣短命夭壽由持此呪
<lb ed="D" n="0013a02"/>信心清淨業障消除更增壽命。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a03"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">末法中一字心呪</cb:mulu><head>末法中一字心呪<note place="inline">染字函</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a04"/><p xml:id="pD10p0013a0401" cb:type="dharani">部林<note place="inline">去聲轉舌</note></p>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a05"/><p xml:id="pD10p0013a0501">此呪能令自法速得成就一切菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>所
<lb ed="D" n="0013a06"/>共讚歎誦念之處於四方面五百驛內
<lb ed="D" n="0013a07"/>一切惡<g ref="#CB29806"/>皆自馳散乃至會中無量菩
<lb ed="D" n="0013a08"/><g ref="#CB16765"/>天龍八部等白佛言我等誓當擁護
<lb ed="D" n="0013a09"/>此呪若見受持讀誦書寫供養愛念思
<lb ed="D" n="0013a10"/>求者當與擁衛令無災患國土安寧財
<lb ed="D" n="0013a11"/>穀豐熟無諸饑饉疾疫不祥。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0013a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">無量壽如來心真言</cb:mulu><head>無量壽如來心真言<note place="inline">漆字函</note></head>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0014a" n="0014a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a01"/><p xml:id="pD10p0014a0101" cb:type="dharani">唵　阿蜜㗚<note place="inline">二合</note>多帝際賀囉吽</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a02"/><p xml:id="pD10p0014a0201">誦滿十萬徧得見阿彌陀如來命終決
<lb ed="D" n="0014a03"/>定得生極樂𠀍界。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a04"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">無量壽佛<g ref="#CB22072"/>往生淨土呪</cb:mulu><head>無量壽佛<g ref="#CB22072"/>往生淨土呪</head>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a05"/><p xml:id="pD10p0014a0501" cb:type="dharani">南無阿彌多婆夜　哆他伽哆夜　哆
<lb ed="D" n="0014a06"/>地夜他　阿彌唎都婆毗　阿彌唎哆
<lb ed="D" n="0014a07"/>悉躭婆毗　阿彌唎哆　毗迦蘭帝
<lb ed="D" n="0014a08"/>　阿彌唎哆　毗迦蘭哆　伽彌𧸐　伽
<lb ed="D" n="0014a09"/>伽那　枳多迦<g ref="#CB27601"/>　莎婆訶</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0014a10"/><p xml:id="pD10p0014a1001">誦此呪者阿彌陀佛常住其頂命終之
<lb ed="D" n="0014a11"/>後任運往生龍樹菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>願生安養夢感
<lb ed="D" n="0014a12"/>此呪。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0015a" n="0015a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0015a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">六字大陀羅尼</cb:mulu><head><note n="0015a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">六字【CB】，<unclear/><unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0015a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">六字</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/><unclear/></rdg></app>大陀羅尼<note place="inline">知字</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0015a02"/><p xml:id="pD10p0015a0201" cb:type="dharani">唵　婆髻䭾那<note place="inline">上</note>莫</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0015a03"/><p xml:id="pD10p0015a0301">此文殊師利六字呪若日日常誦莫忘
<lb ed="D" n="0015a04"/>定受業報亦令消滅若日別誦一百八
<lb ed="D" n="0015a05"/>徧臨命終時得見文殊師利隨願受生。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0015a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">文殊師利根本一字呪</cb:mulu><head>文殊師利根本一字呪<note place="inline">才字函</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0015a07"/><p xml:id="pD10p0015a0701" cb:type="dharani">唵　齒臨<note place="inline">去聲</note></p>
<lb ed="D" n="0015a08"/><p xml:id="pD10p0015a0801">此呪能滅一切惡邪魍魎是一切佛吉
<lb ed="D" n="0015a09"/>祥之法亦能成就一切神呪誦此呪者
<lb ed="D" n="0015a10"/>能令眾生起大慈悲一切障閡皆得消
<lb ed="D" n="0015a11"/>滅所有諸願皆得滿足乃至見𠀍當來
<lb ed="D" n="0015a12"/>常獲安隱與諸如來大菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>常為眷屬。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0016a" n="0016a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0016a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">文殊五字呪</cb:mulu><head>文殊五字呪<note place="inline">府字函</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0016a02"/><p xml:id="pD10p0016a0201" cb:type="dharani">阿囉跛佐曩</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0016a03"/><p xml:id="pD10p0016a0301">若誦此呪一徧如誦八萬四千十二韋
<lb ed="D" n="0016a04"/>陀藏經依法常誦者功德無量。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0016a05"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">普賢菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>滅罪呪</cb:mulu><head>普賢菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>滅罪呪<note place="inline">良字函</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0016a06"/><p xml:id="pD10p0016a0601" cb:type="dharani">支波啄<note place="inline">決定</note><note place="inline">一</note>　毗尼波啄<note place="inline">断結</note><note place="inline">二</note>　烏蘇波啄
<lb ed="D" n="0016a07"/><note place="inline">生盡</note><note place="inline">三</note></p>
<lb ed="D" n="0016a08"/><p xml:id="pD10p0016a0801">平旦七徧夜七徧誦此呪去厭魅野道
<lb ed="D" n="0016a09"/>蠱毒能得身心慧三解脫後生不受生
<lb ed="D" n="0016a10"/>死身得法身常身一切惡人惡<g ref="#CB29806"/>毒獸
<lb ed="D" n="0016a11"/>等聞此呪聲悉皆口噤不相惱亂。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0016a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">觀自在菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>如意心呪</cb:mulu><head>觀自在菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>如意心呪<note place="inline">才字函</note></head>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0017a" n="0017a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0017a01"/><p xml:id="pD10p0017a0101">南無佛䭾耶南無達磨耶南無僧伽耶
<lb ed="D" n="0017a02"/>南無觀自在菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>摩訶<g ref="#CB16765"/>具大悲心者。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0017a03"/><p xml:id="pD10p0017a0301" cb:type="dharani">怛姪他菴斫羯羅　伐底震多末尼莫
<lb ed="D" n="0017a04"/>訶鉢蹬䛧　嚕嚕嚕嚕　底瑟侘<note place="inline">丑嫁切</note>
<lb ed="D" n="0017a05"/>篅<note place="inline">市恱切</note>攞痾羯利沙也　吽　癹莎訶</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0017a06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">大心呪</cb:mulu><head>大心呪</head><p xml:id="pD10p0017a0604" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">菴鉢蹋摩震多末尼篅攞吽</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0017a07"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">隨心呪</cb:mulu><head>隨心呪</head><p xml:id="pD10p0017a0704" cb:type="dharani" rend="inline">菴跋喇陀　鉢亶<note place="inline">多旱切</note>䛧吽</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0017a08"/><p xml:id="pD10p0017a0801">若人希求此生現報者應當一心受持
<lb ed="D" n="0017a09"/>此呪欲受持時不問日月星辰吉凶并
<lb ed="D" n="0017a10"/>別修齋戒亦不假洗浴及以淨衣但止
<lb ed="D" n="0017a11"/>攝心口誦不懈百千種事所願皆成更
<lb ed="D" n="0017a12"/>無明呪能得與此如意呪王勢力齊者
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0018a" n="0018a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0018a01"/>是故先當除諸罪障次能成就一切事
<lb ed="D" n="0018a02"/>業亦能消除五逆重罪一切病苦不祥
<lb ed="D" n="0018a03"/>事等若日日誦一百八徧即見觀自在
<lb ed="D" n="0018a04"/>菩<g ref="#CB16765"/>告言善男子汝等勿怖欲求何願
<lb ed="D" n="0018a05"/>一切施汝乃至即得自身清淨常為諸
<lb ed="D" n="0018a06"/>王公𡖖宰輔恭敬供養眾人愛敬在所
<lb ed="D" n="0018a07"/>生處常得宿命始從今日乃至成佛不
<lb ed="D" n="0018a08"/>墮惡道常生佛前。</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0018a09"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">蓮華部心呪</cb:mulu><head>蓮華部心呪<note place="inline"><g ref="#CB06224"/>字函</note></head>
<lb ed="D" n="0018a10"/><p xml:id="pD10p0018a1001" cb:type="dharani">唵　阿嚕力迦<note place="inline">半音呼之</note>莎嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>訶</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0018a11"/><p xml:id="pD10p0018a1101">觀自在菩<g ref="#CB16765"/><g ref="#CB22072"/>此呪<note n="0018a1101" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【國圖】</note><app n="0018a1101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">巳</rdg></app>白佛言𠀍尊此
<lb ed="D" n="0018a12"/>真言是一切蓮華部心若每日晨朝於
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0019a" n="0019a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0019a01"/>我像前<note n="0019a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">作【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0019a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">作</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>曼茶羅散種種華誦八千徧
<lb ed="D" n="0019a02"/><note n="0019a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">後【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0019a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">後</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>不與人語更誦多少漸為強記若依
<lb ed="D" n="0019a03"/>此法能滿六月即大聦明凡所聞言皆
<lb ed="D" n="0019a04"/>領不忘若清淨洗浴而於佛前造三圎
<lb ed="D" n="0019a05"/>壇一佛二法弟三為僧各如法供養手
<lb ed="D" n="0019a06"/>執香鑪燒香獻<note n="0019a0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">已【CB】，巳【國圖】</note><app n="0019a0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">已</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">巳</rdg></app>誦滿八千徧應墯地
<lb ed="D" n="0019a07"/>獄四重五逆一切重罪無不消滅必不
<lb ed="D" n="0019a08"/>疑也若滿六月𣫭誦一千五百徧所有
<lb ed="D" n="0019a09"/>悉地皆得成就。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0019a10"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0019a11"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="1"><cb:jhead>尊勝等靈異神呪共二十道</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
<lb ed="D" n="0019a12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">跋</cb:mulu>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0020a" n="0020a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0020a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">德求跋</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pD10p0020a0101"><note n="0020a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">惠雲【CB】，<unclear/><unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0020a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">惠雲</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/><unclear/></rdg></app>院釋迦遺教比丘德求乾道九年太歲
<lb ed="D" n="0020a02"/>癸巳季春時年五十有九歲謹以自己衣鉢
<lb ed="D" n="0020a03"/>錢<note n="0020a0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">重【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0020a0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">重</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>新修　釋迦如來舎利<g ref="#CB30988"/><g ref="#CB30259"/>二所并
<lb ed="D" n="0020a04"/>印造　尊勝<g ref="#CB21717"/>祕文奉安<g ref="#CB30988"/><g ref="#CB30259"/>之<note n="0020a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">內【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0020a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">內</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>願
<lb ed="D" n="0020a05"/>諸天大權於空中守護此<g ref="#CB30988"/><g ref="#CB30259"/>令其堅
<lb ed="D" n="0020a06"/><note n="0020a0601" resp="CBETA" type="add">固【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0020a0601"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">固</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>久住𠀍間莫使天魔侵害令人天瞻<note n="0020a0602" resp="CBETA" type="add">仰【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0020a0602"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">仰</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="D" n="0020a07"/>平等普熏四㤙<g ref="#CB21717"/>報三有普資法<note n="0020a0701" resp="CBETA" type="add">界【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0020a0701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">界</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="D" n="0020a08"/><unclear/><unclear/>霑斯利然後父母師僧早願<unclear/><unclear/>
<lb ed="D" n="0020a09"/><unclear/><unclear/>求臨終正念視聴分明如入禪㝎隱几
<lb ed="D" n="0020a10"/><unclear/><unclear/>無業障袈裟之下乞無魔<unclear/><unclear/><unclear/>
<lb ed="D" n="0020a11"/><unclear/><unclear/>佛力<g ref="#CB15891"/>熏早悟大乘心開意解<unclear/>
<lb ed="D" n="0020a12"/><unclear/><unclear/>悟明心地求願徃生德求謹願。</p></cb:div>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D10.8814.0021a" n="0021a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0021a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">魏謙升跋</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pD10p0021a0101">謝氏肇淛五雜組云書所以貴宋版者不
<lb ed="D" n="0021a02"/>惟點畫無譌亦且箋刻精好若法帖然凡
<lb ed="D" n="0021a03"/>宋刻有肥瘦二種肥者學顏瘦者學歐行
<lb ed="D" n="0021a04"/>款疏密任意不一而字勢皆生動此尊勝等
<lb ed="D" n="0021a05"/>靈異神咒共二十道乃宋孝宗乾道九年秀州
<lb ed="D" n="0021a06"/>恵雲院僧徳求裝治供奉釋迦如来舍利寶
<lb ed="D" n="0021a07"/><g ref="#CB30259"/>內者墖既<note n="0021a0701" resp="CBETA" type="add">圮【CB】，𡉏【國圖】</note><app n="0021a0701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">圮</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">𡉏</rdg></app>遂流落人間有當日徳求自
<lb ed="D" n="0021a08"/>䟦墨迹如新書法秀逸似張樗寮其咒語書
<lb ed="D" n="0021a09"/>刻皆精是瘦者學歐一類雲窗展誦古香古
<lb ed="D" n="0021a10"/>色塵心為之䪺清見者當作法帖觀不可徒
<lb ed="D" n="0021a11"/>以尋常經𠕋視之。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0021a12"/><p xml:id="pD10p0021a1201" rend="margin-left:1em">道光二十九年七月既望錢唐魏謙升滋伯記</p></cb:div>
