<lb ed="D" n="0022a01"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">張爾田跋</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pD10p0022a0101"><note n="0022a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">右【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0022a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">右</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>宋刊尊勝陀羅尼大灌頂光真言首楞嚴心呪廣大寶樓閣陀羅尼根
<lb ed="D" n="0022a02"/>本呪禮<note n="0022a0201" resp="CBETA" type="add">拜【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0022a0201"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">拜</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>滅罪呪金剛壽命陀羅尼一字心呪無量心真言六字大陀羅尼根
<lb ed="D" n="0022a03"/>本一字呪文殊五字呪普賢滅罪呪如意心呪蓮花心呪等共二十道皆從密部
<lb ed="D" n="0022a04"/><unclear/>出<unclear/>便誦<unclear/>以覈令藏文身<unclear/>身音表<unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/>數碩異攷道宣內典錄
<lb ed="D" n="0022a05"/>明<unclear/>刊定記大都<unclear/>詳部偶<unclear/>紀<unclear/>記<unclear/>號智昇開元釋錄<unclear/><unclear/>藏收<unclear/><unclear/><unclear/>錄四卷
<lb ed="D" n="0022a06"/>不詳<unclear/><unclear/>所刪非列<unclear/>字蓋是後人存載非昇師原本唯釋恒安唐保大間續貞
<lb ed="D" n="0022a07"/>元目錄志以千文<unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/>随<unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/>此然浙本<unclear/>本<unclear/>合分配<unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/>
<lb ed="D" n="0022a08"/><unclear/>比邱<unclear/>瑩所辨今之龍藏<unclear/><unclear/>南北<unclear/><unclear/>勝明<unclear/><unclear/>幸較此冊<unclear/><unclear/>鈔
<lb ed="D" n="0022a09"/><unclear/>就其<unclear/>列<unclear/>可攷是<unclear/><unclear/>舊次所謂<unclear/><unclear/>式者或在於茲洵瓌寶矣徳
<lb ed="D" n="0022a10"/><unclear/><unclear/>履散<unclear/><unclear/>題墨疏<unclear/>無座<unclear/><unclear/>餐味<g ref="#CB09168"/>疲淵<unclear/>湛然樂盦居士其
<lb ed="D" n="0022a11"/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/>酉春二月錢唐鄔波索迦張爾田孟<note n="0022a1101" resp="CBETA" type="add">劬【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0022a1101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">劬</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>敬䟦。</p></cb:div></cb:div>
